          √úr√ºnleri d√ºzenleyebilir ve alƒ±≈üveri≈üe devam edebilirsin. G√∂rseller y√ºksek √ß√∂z√ºn√ºrl√ºkte saklanƒ±r.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16">
      <% 
        const totalItems = cart.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.qty, 0);
        const totalAmount = cart.reduce((sum, item) => {
          const price = Number(item.price || 0);
          return sum + price * item.qty;
        }, 0);
      %>

      <% if (cart.length === 0) { %>
        <div class="card glass text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Sepetin bo≈ü</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">
            √úr√ºnleri eklemek i√ßin katalogdan favorilerini se√ßebilir veya trend listemize g√∂z atabilirsin.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/products"
            class="btn-primary">
            √úr√ºnlere Git
          </a>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[2fr,1fr]">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <% cart.forEach(item => { %>
              <div class="card glass flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="img-frame w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <a href="/products/<%= item.id %>" aria-label="<%= item.name %>">
                      <% if (item.image_url) { %>
                        <img src="<%= item.image_url %>" alt="<%= item.name %>" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                      <% } else { %>
                        <span class="text-xl">üì¶</span>
                      <% } %>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                  <p class="text-base font-semibold"><a href="/products/<%= item.id %>" class="hover:text-indigo-600"><%= item.name %></a></p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">
                    Adet: <%= item.qty %>
                  </p>
                  <% if ((item.discountPercent || 0) > 0 && item.originalPrice) { %>
                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">
                      <span class="line-through text-slate-400">‚Ç∫<%= Number(item.originalPrice || 0).toFixed(2) %></span>
                      <span class="ml-2 font-semibold text-emerald-600">ƒ∞ndirimli birim: ‚Ç∫<%= Number(item.price || 0).toFixed(2) %> (-<%= item.discountPercent %>%)</span>
                    </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Birim fiyat: ‚Ç∫<%= Number(item.price || 0).toFixed(2) %></p>
                    <% } %>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-700 mt-1 font-semibold">
                    Toplam (indirimli): ‚Ç∫<%= (Number(item.price || 0) * item.qty).toFixed(2) %>
                  </p>
                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <form action="/cart/update/<%= item.id %>" method="POST" class="flex items-center gap-2" oninput="this.submit()">
                    <label for="qty-<%= item.id %>" class="sr-only">Adet</label>
                    <input
                      id="qty-<%= item.id %>"
                      name="qty"
                      type="number"
                      min="0"
                      value="<%= item.qty %>"
                      class="w-16 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 px-2 py-1 text-sm"
                    />
                    <button type="submit" class="text-xs text-indigo-600 font-semibold hover:underline">G√ºncelle</button>
                  </form>
                  <a
                    href="/cart/remove/<%= item.id %>"
                    class="text-xs text-rose-600 hover:underline">
                    Kaldƒ±r
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% }) %>
          </div>

          <div class="card glass h-fit">
            <p class="section-label text-slate-500 mb-3">√ñzet</p>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">Toplam √ºr√ºn</span>
              <span class="text-base font-semibold"><%= totalItems %></span>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">Toplam tutar</span>
              <span class="text-base font-semibold">
                ‚Ç∫<%= totalAmount.toFixed(2) %>
              </span>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-6">
              Fiyatlar bilgilendirme ama√ßlƒ±dƒ±r, nihai ko≈üullar satƒ±≈ü temsilcisi ile netle≈üir.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <a
                href="/checkout"
